<p><b>Kleptocracy</b> (sometimes <i>cleptocracy</i>, occasionally <i>kleptarchy</i>) is a term applied to a <a href="/wiki/Form_of_government" title="Form of government">government</a> that extends the personal wealth and political power of government officials and the ruling class (collectively, <i>kleptocrats</i>) at the expense of the population, sometimes without even the pretense of honest service. The term derives from the Greek root <i>klepto</i> (theft).</p>
